    {
      "id": "onboarding-mindset",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Core Mindset",
      "position": {
        "x": -1000,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Core Mindset\n\n- Graphs are shared memory\n- Every mutation has consequences\n- Preserve intent before improving form\n- Never surprise future readers (human or agent)\n\nYou are editing **history**, not pixels.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
