    {
      "id": "onboarding-howto",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "How to Work in a Graph",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## How to Work in a Graph\n\n1. Read the Manifest first\n2. Run validation before mutation\n3. Prefer transformation skills over manual edits\n4. Leave notes when intent changes\n5. Keep diffs small and meaningful\n\nWork as if someone else will inherit this tomorrow.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
