    {
      "id": "onboarding-continuity",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Continuity Expectations",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Continuity Expectations\n\n- Do not delete history casually\n- Use refactors instead of rewrites\n- Respect schema versions\n- Never break execution silently\n\nContinuity is kindness to the future.",
